        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "(46) ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "The men of the tower of Shechem.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "—Evidently the garrison of the house of Millo (",
        "children": []
